+Sg  !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Singular number
+Du  !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Dual number
+Pl  !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Plural number
+Ess !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Essive case
+Nom !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Nominative case
+Gen !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Genitive case
+Acc !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Accusative case
+Ill !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Illative case
+Loc !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Locative case
+Com !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Comitative case
+Ine !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Inesive case
+Ela !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Elative case
+Par !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Partitive case
+Abe !!вүҲ *  **@CODE@** = Abessive case

!! ## Possessive tags

 +PxSg1  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix singular first person
 +PxSg2  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix singular second person
 +PxSg3  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix singular third person
 +PxDu1  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix dual first person
 +PxDu2  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix dual second person
 +PxDu3  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix dual third person
 +PxPl1  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix plural first person
 +PxPl2  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix plural second person
 +PxPl3  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** possessive suffix plural plural person

