 +Sem/Part        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Feature, part of something; half, part, percent, rest, tenth
 +Sem/Perc-cogn   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Cloth
 +Sem/Perc-emo    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Emotional perception; fear, feeling of identity, empathy, sadness, working motivation
 +Sem/Perc-phys   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Physical perception; shoulder pain, gass smell, sleep (during the night), need of sleep, hunger
 +Sem/Perc-psych  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Psychic perception
 +Sem/Plant       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Plant; lichen, plant, cucumber, bluebell, poisonous mushroom
 +Sem/Plantpart   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Plant part; twig, leaf, root, seed, pine trunk
 +Sem/Play        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Play
 +Sem/Plc         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Place; world, nature, airport, workplace, fireplace
 +Sem/Plc-abstr   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Abstract place; bachelor level, job market, third place, Troms website, address
 +Sem/Plc-elevate !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Elevated place; mountain, peak, mountain top, scree, volcano
 +Sem/Plc-line    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Place limitations; national border, border, finish line, stop line, equator
 +Sem/Plc-water   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Water; river, lake, polar sea, sea, well
 +Sem/Pos         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Position (as in social position job); 50% position, presidency, fixed position, kindergarten place, role in society
 +Sem/Process     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Process
 +Sem/Prod        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Product
 +Sem/Prod-audio  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Audio product; yoik, roar, Beatles song, Bible psalm, blues
 +Sem/Prod-cogn   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Cognition product; thought, decision, knowledge, lack of understanding, requirement
 +Sem/Prod-ling   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Linguistic product; message, question, agreement, translation, criticism
 +Sem/Prod-vis    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Visual product; picture, film, TV series, documentary, art
 +Sem/Rel         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Relation; relation, dependency, subordination, analogy, equivalence
 +Sem/Route       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Route-like place; street, path, corridor, bridge, winter path
 +Sem/Rule        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Rule or convention; cultural tradition, abortion law, EU rule, law of cosines, fair play
 +Sem/Semcon      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Abstract semantic concept; result, objective, reason, alternative, case
 +Sem/Sign        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Sign (e.g. numbers, punctuation); ID number, ДҢSV letters, quotation mark, hieroglyph, symbol
 +Sem/Sport       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Sport; table tennis, judo, motor cross, ice hockey, floorball
 +Sem/State       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = State; hurry, captivity, anarchy, biodiversity, chaos
 +Sem/State-sick  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Illness; allergy, cold, autism, dementia, somnambulism
 +Sem/Substnc     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Substance; Water, sand, air, smoke, carbohydrate, vitamin, dust
 +Sem/Sur         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Surname
 +Sem/Symbol      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Symbol
 +Sem/Time        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Time; ГЎigi time, April, half an hour, Tuesday, deadline
 +Sem/Time-clock  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Time
 +Sem/Tool        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Prototypical tool for repairing things; axe, knife, fire striker, plastic hammer, wrench
 +Sem/Tool-catch  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Tool used for catching; artificial fly, fishing net for cod, fishing rod, lasso used in wintertime, mouse trap
 +Sem/Tool-clean  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Tool used for cleaning; broom, vegetable brush, toothbrush, cleaning equipment
 +Sem/Tool-it     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Tool used in IT/tool within IT; IT infrastructure, analyzer, searching function, computer program, browser
 +Sem/Tool-measr  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Tool used for measuring; barometer, hourglass, ruler, spirit level, scale
 +Sem/Tool-music  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Musical instrument; shaman drum, guitar, violin, musical instrument, jaw harp
 +Sem/Tool-write  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Writing tool; colored pen, pencil, chalk, paintbrush, paint
 +Sem/Txt         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Written document; paper, book, letter, e-mail, song
 +Sem/Veh         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Vehicle; car, boat, sled, vehicle, draft reindeer, bicycle
 +Sem/Wpn         !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Weapon; rifle, bow, sword, arrow, war axe
 +Sem/Wthr        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = The Weather or the state of ground; cloudy weather, wind, driving conditions, night sunlight, rain shower
 +Sem/Year        !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** = Year


